  <source>Rigshospitalet, Denmark</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis is that surgery is of benefit in locally advanced NSCLC with N2 disease.

      Patients are randomised to surgery or not.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients are after staging randomised to neoadj. chemotherapy followed by surgery followed by
      irradiation or to chemotherapy followed by irradiation.

      Endpoint is survival.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
