  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Histologically verified NSCLC

          -  Stage IIIA/N2

          -  age 18-75

          -  Lung function test allowing surgery

          -  Mediastinoscopy performed

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prior chemotherapy

          -  Prior irradiation
      </textblock>
